      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Kunai Ask You a Favor?",
        "Client": "Kunai Hurler Extraordinaire",
        "Description": "I have mastered the kunai! Swords?\r\nBows? Hah! Don\u0027t need \u0027em! ...Well,\r\nat least, I thought I didn\u0027t until those\r\nmonsters put me face down, tassets\r\nup in a cart back to camp. Avenge\r\nmy bruised behind and I\u0027ll teach you\r\nmy kunai-accentuated poses!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Barroth, a Rathian\r\nand a Diablos",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Kun... a\u00EFe ?",
        "Client": "Lanceur de kunai dou\u00E9",
        "Description": "Je suis pass\u00E9 ma\u00EEtre dans l\u0027art des\r\nkunai ! Une \u00E9p\u00E9e ? Un arc ? Pff, pas\r\nbesoin ! Enfin... c\u0027est ce que je\r\ncroyais jusqu\u0027\u00E0 ce que des monstres\r\nme mettent la p\u00E2t\u00E9e. Venge-moi\r\net je t\u0027apprendrai des poses\r\nli\u00E9es aux kunai !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Barroth, une Rathian\r\net un Diablos",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Di kunai e vendette",
        "Client": "Lanciatore esperto di kunai",
        "Description": "Ho padroneggiato il kunai!\r\nSpade? Archi? Inutili! O almeno\r\nlo pensavo, poi quei mostri mi\r\nhanno mandato gambe all\u0027aria\r\nsu un carro per l\u0027accampamento.\r\nVendica il mio sedere ammaccato\r\ne ti insegner\u00F2 le mie pose kunai!",
        "Target": "Caccia un Barroth, una Rathian\r\ne un Diablos",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Eine Kunai-ne Bitte",
        "Client": "Spitzen-Kunai-Werfer",
        "Description": "Ich habe das Kunai gemeistert!\r\nSchwerter? Bogen? Ha! Brauch\r\nich nicht! ... So war es, bis\r\nmir diese Monster den Po\r\nversohlt und mich ins Lager\r\ngejagt haben. R\u00E4che mich, dann\r\nlehre ich dich Kunai-Posen!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Barroth, eine Rathian und\r\neinen Diablos.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Los kunai son lo mejor",
        "Client": "Experto lanzador de kunai",
        "Description": "\u00A1Domino los kunai a las mil\r\nmaravillas! No necesito arcos\r\no espadas. Aunque... igual me\r\nhabr\u00EDan ido bien cuando me\r\natacaron esos monstruos.\r\n\u00A1Te ense\u00F1o mis poses de kunai\r\nsi les das una lecci\u00F3n por m\u00ED!",
        "Target": "Caza un Barroth, una Rathian\r\ny un Diablos",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u0421\u0434\u0435\u043B\u0430\u0435\u0448\u044C \u043E\u0434\u043E\u043B\u0436\u0435\u043D\u0438\u0435?",
